Package org.codehaus.mojo.license.api

Api package

This package contains api to be used by mojos.

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MavenProjectDependenciesConfigurator
    Contract to configure which dependencies will be loaded by the dependency tool via the method DependenciesTool#loadProjectDependencies(org.apache.maven.project.MavenProject, MavenProjectDependenciesConfigurator, org.apache.maven.artifact.repository.ArtifactRepository, List, java.util.SortedMap)
    ThirdPartyDetails
    Details of a artifact about his third-parties stuff.
    ThirdPartyHelper
    Helper class that provides common functionality required by both the mojos and the reports.
    ThirdPartyTool
    A tool to load third party files missing files.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArtifactFilters
    Artifact filtering by groupId:artifactId regular expression includes/excludes Scope includes/excludes Type includes/excludes
    ArtifactFilters.Builder
    An ArtifactFilters builder.
    DefaultThirdPartyDetails
    Default implementation of ThirdPartyDetails.
    DefaultThirdPartyHelper
    Default implementation of the ThirdPartyHelper.
    DefaultThirdPartyTool
    Default implementation of the third party tool.
    DependenciesTool
    A tool to deal with dependencies of a project.
    FreeMarkerHelper
    A helper to deal with freemarker templating.
    ResolvedProjectDependencies
    Copies of the project's dependency sets.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DependenciesToolException
    Created on 23/05/16.
    ThirdPartyToolException
    An exception occurring during the execution of this tool.
